### 测试说明
# 本地启动了一个 Streamable HTTP MCP 服务: http://0.0.0.0:8000/mcp
# 通过 SSE 接口透明代理使用该服务

### 1a. 检查服务状态 - 自动检测后端协议（推荐）
# 不指定 backendProtocol，系统会自动检测远程服务的协议类型
POST http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/check_status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mcpId": "test-streamable-service-auto",
  "mcpJsonConfig": "{\"mcpServers\": {\"test-service\": {\"url\": \"http://127.0.0.1:8000/mcp\"}}}",
  "mcpType": "Persistent"
}

### 1b. 检查服务状态 - 手动指定后端协议
# 如果你确定后端协议类型，可以手动指定 backendProtocol
POST http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/check_status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mcpId": "test-streamable-service-manual",
  "mcpJsonConfig": "{\"mcpServers\": {\"test-service\": {\"url\": \"http://127.0.0.1:8000/mcp\"}}}",
  "mcpType": "Persistent",
  "backendProtocol": "Stream"
}

### 2. 获取 SSE 连接（使用自动检测的服务）
# 客户端使用 SSE 协议连接，代理内部会自动转换为 Streamable HTTP 协议
GET http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/proxy/test-streamable-service-auto/sse
Accept: text/event-stream

### 3. 发送消息到 MCP 服务 - initialize
POST http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/proxy/test-streamable-service-auto/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "msg-1",
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {
      "name": "test-client",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}

### 4. 列出可用工具
POST http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/proxy/test-streamable-service-auto/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "msg-2",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}

### 5. 调用工具 (根据实际可用的工具调整)
POST http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/proxy/test-streamable-service-auto/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "msg-3",
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "your-tool-name",
    "arguments": {}
  }
}

### 6. 清理服务（自动检测版本）
DELETE http://localhost:8085/mcp/config/delete/test-streamable-service-auto
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 7. 清理服务（手动指定版本）
DELETE http://localhost:8085/mcp/config/delete/test-streamable-service-manual
Content-Type: application/json

{}
